Class Resource

java.lang.Object
com.example.projectfx.resources.Resource
All Implemented Interfaces:
Consumable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Algae, Fruits, Grass
public abstract class Resource extends Object implements Consumable
Abstract class representing a resource in the ecosystem. A resource has a type, quantity, position, and an image. It can be consumed and regenerated over time.
